Generate (almost usable) default wrappers from header:
 grep '^ *extern' /usr/include/unistd.h | sed 's/extern \([^ ]*\)/IC_GENERIC(\1/;s/^\([^ ]*\) \*/\1* /;s/ \([^ ]*\) (/, \1, (/;s/).*/),\n           {ret = orig_fn(XXX);})/'

Test wether FireBuild intercepts all syscalls:
firebuild -i strace  -o/tmp/ls.trace ls
awk 'BEGIN {SKIP=0}
     /firebuild-intercept-begin/ {SKIP=1; next}
     /firebuild-intercept-end/ {SKIP=0; next}
     {if (SKIP == 0 ) { print $0 } else {next;}}'  /tmp/ls.trace

